  <main>
    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/chapter-2/article-xii/division-2/section-sec.-2.111"
             temporalId="sSEC_ 2_111">
      <num>SEC. 2.111</num>
      <heading>Recordkeeping and inspection</heading>
      <content>
        <p>a.</p>
        <p>Committees shall keep complete and accurate records or documents evidencing compliance
               with this division.</p>
        <p>b.</p>
        <p>The city may request and inspect, at no cost to the city, any records or documents
               for enforcement of and compliance with this division.</p>
        <p>(Ord. No. 5.22, § 5, 4/26/22.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
  </main>
